hudson.model.StringParameterDefinition.name: BRANCH_PREFIX
hudson.model.StringParameterDefinition.description: A branch prefix, for example 'feature' in 'feature/1337-coolfeature'. Used in job names and as git branch specifier formatted as 'refs/heads/${branch_prefix}/${branch_name}'.

hudson.model.StringParameterDefinition.name: BRANCH_NAME
hudson.model.StringParameterDefinition.description: A branch name, for example '1337-coolfeature' in 'feature/1337-coolfeature'. Used in job names and as git branch specifier formatted as 'refs/heads/${branch_prefix}/${branch_name}'.

hudson.model.StringParameterDefinition.name: PIPELINE
hudson.model.StringParameterDefinition.description: Comma-separated list of jobs in a pipeline
